references: As shown in Table I, our meta-controller achieves a higher success rate and lower dynamic grasping time, due to three factors. (1) It can reason about the reachable workspace and through dynamically controlling the look-ahead time and time budget, it maintains the predicted pose and the planned motion within the most reachable region. (2) It learns to generate a small look-ahead time when the predicted trajectory is not accurate. (3) It learns to produce a small but sufficient time budget for motion planning.
